OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMist and fog clearing to leave
OL,6,Fbright and sunny spells for many.
OL,7,FStaying very warm in light winds for
OL,8,Fmany for the time of year but
OL,9,Ftemperatures slightly lower than of
OL,10,Flate.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA mostly dry start to the
OL,13,Fnight with high cloud around. Light
OL,14,Frain in the west in the early hours,
OL,15,Fbut a much more comfortable night for
OL,16,Fmany.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
