OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FLow cloud to start with, but
OL,6,Flifting through the morning and into
OL,7,Fthe afternoon. Isolated showers
OL,8,Fdeveloping, with sunny spells in
OL,9,Fbetween. Warm, but cooler than of late.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FScattered showers continuing into
OL,13,FMonday with heavy rain, possible
OL,14,Fthunderstorms with a mix of hail.
OL,15,FStaying unsettled through the week as
OL,16,Ftemperatures return to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
